URL: https://github.com/Mosquito-Alert/VectorModelR,
    https://labs.mosquitoalert.com/VectorModelR/
BugReports: https://github.com/Mosquito-Alert/VectorModelR/issues
Description: A set of tools for accessing global datasets, and combining them with Mosquito Alert citizen science data to generate Vector Models (<https://www.mosquitoalert.com/>), including Mosquito Alert citizen science data, smart trap data from the Irideon Senscape API, and traditional mosquito trap data. 
